data.title: Providing for congressional disapproval under chapter 8 of title 5, United States Code, of the rule submitted by the Department of Education relating to "Improving Income Driven Repayment for the Will
data.meta_description: Analysis of public record to itemize the work of elected members of Congress in the United States of America, and provide an online tool for their constituents to spread the word about it. Take a look at what bills your senators and house representatives are working on today.
